        "id": "50bc59c99a8489ee",
        "text": "Robin Asby\nRetired academic, consultant, and researcher; he achieved a PhD in mathematical physics in 1968; for the last 35 years his research has focused on [[systems thinking]] and [[cybernetics]], and its underpinning philosophy, and in particular its application to learning, [[governing]] and quantum theory."
