        "text": "# Bibliography\nAristotle (1986). De Anima. Trans. H. Lawson-\nTancred. London: Penguin Books.\n\nAsby, R. (2021). Thinking Systems: An Organic\nLanguage of Harmony for Human\nSurvival. Charmouth: Triarchy Press."
