        "id": "6206287e5dd2811e",
        "text": "# The Relationship Between the Object Frame and the Process Frame\nThe foundation of the systemic process modelling approach defines a model as a system that produces \na particular output from a given input in a brain and nervous system. This aligns with the holistic reasoning of Henrich et al. (2010):"
