      "item": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "id": "8eb3a8fdd960bb00",
        "text": "# On the Framing of Systems and Cybernetic Models"
      },
      "date": 1700600077964
    },
    {
      "item": {
        "type": "factory",
        "id": "8eb3a8fdd960bb00"
